filterList.name: filter list setting
filterList.description[zh_CN]: 此配置为设置需要过滤掉的上报窗口的名单，具体上报的信息是窗口从创建到完成绘制消耗的时间
filterList.description: This configuration is to set a filter list for reporting windows. The specific information reported is the time it takes from creation to completion of drawing of the window.
